{"tid":1540263,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"啱啱放工 有人挨住我訓覺","createTime":"2019-09-04T11:08:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T13:21:31.000Z","uid":205742,"like":20,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"fab8f8eed4e699a4e17246c09896e23165490e75","tid":1540263,"uid":205742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:08:24.000Z","msg":"嗰時搭緊地鐵返屋企 咁好好彩搵到個位坐 坐坐下 發現自己個膊頭比人撞咗幾下 一另去右面 就發現有個文青look嘅大學生涯住我膊頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 嗰時即刻扮冇野 繼續比佢捱住我嗰個軟淋淋好舒服嘅膊頭 嗰時偷偷地望下佢 見到佢拎住部電腦 著住條長裙 戴眼鏡咁樣 著住對啡色皮鞋同藍色襪 <br />\n<br />\n真係着得好好睇呀你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之後為咗享受多段時間 我到站都唔落車<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 就為咗喺耳邊同佢講一句「小姐 到站啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」<br />\n<br />\n佢好怕醜咁卒住眼咁答「嗯....」 <br />\n<br />\n然之後我就頭也不回咁樣行出車廂門口 搭電梯落去下一層 搭返轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我唔係壞人嚟 雖然咁樣上連登打文好變態<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我無掂過你<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43065c810a32050d75a3d2f5f8fa7c14f7ced592","tid":1540263,"uid":230890,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:09:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9a2557c27fe2f1551d3e33f7def8cbd10a9a4e06","tid":1540263,"uid":258566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:10:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d665e8daa67b07ffa7f0f5e026a2eec09aae2002","tid":1540263,"uid":205742,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:10:22.000Z","msg":"唔好拉我呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 除非你想揾返我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢度我contact tg:<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n記得唔好